DOC.brief_summary: The objective study compare clinical performance ProClear 1-Day versus 1-Day Acuvue Moist one week daily disposable wear .
DOC.brief_title: Multi-center Clinical Evaluation PC 1-Day v 1-Day Acuvue Moist
DOC.detailed_description: The purpose cross-over study evaluate clinical performance ProClear-1 Day comparison 1-Day Acuvue® Moist® . In particular , study focus lens wear comfort .
DOC.criteria: A person eligible inclusion study he/she : Is 18 40 year age ( inclusive ) Have use mobile phone send receive text message throughout day duration study . Has selfreported visual exam last two year Is adapt soft CL ( Contact Lens ) wearer Must able wear lens least 6 full day 7 day ; 14 hour per day , assume contraindication Has CL spherical prescription 1.00 6.00 ( inclusive ) Has less 0.75D ( Diopters ) spectacle cylinder eye . Is correctable visual acuity 20/25 good eye Has clear cornea active ocular disease Has read , understood sign information consent letter . Is willing comply wear schedule ( least 40 hr per week ) Is willing comply visit schedule A person exclude study he/she : Has never wear contact lens . Currently wear rigid gas permeable contact lens . Has history achieve comfortable CL wear ( 5 day per week ; > 8 hours/day ) Has CL prescription outside range 1.00 6.00D Has spectacle cylinder great 0.50D cylinder either eye . Has best correct spectacle distance vision worse 20/25 either eye . Has systemic disease affect ocular health . Is use systemic topical medication affect ocular health . Has ocular pathology severe insufficiency lacrimal secretion Has persistent , clinically significant corneal conjunctival staining Has active neovascularization central corneal scar . Is aphakic . Is presbyopic . Has undergone corneal refractive surgery . Is participate type eye related clinical research study .
